<p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rlue/i/master/solana/responsive.gif" style="float: right; margin-bottom: 1rem;" /></p>

<h3 id="features">Features</h3>

<ul>
  <li>Compatible with GitHub Pages</li>
  <li>Supports categories &amp; tags</li>
  <li>Responsive design</li>
  <li>Lightweight (no jQuery, Bootstrap, etc.)</li>
  <li>Obfuscates email addresses for protection against email harvesting bots</li>
  <li>Comments via outbound links to Reddit</li>
</ul>

